Exhorted banks to speed-up issuance of RuPay Cards so as to enable weavers access maximum benefit & also move towards digitisation.
So far 23,611 MUDRA loans have been sanctioned by 56 banks to handloom weavers in 19 states.
With products being sold directly to the market and traders, weavers' monthly income has increased by 50% within 5-6 months.
Earlier, weavers were unable to purchase raw materials due to shortage of funds but Weaver MUDRA now enables them to become entrepreneurs.
